sentence: Monday's session closes with the NASDAQ Composite Index at 2,986.96.
The total shares traded for the NASDAQ was over 1.5 billion.
Advancers stocks led declining by 1.34 to 1 ratio.
There were 1417 advancers and 1056 decliners for the day.
On the NASDAQ Stock Exchange 27 stocks reached a 52 week high and 12 those reaching lows totaled.
The most active, advancers, decliners, unusual volume and most active by dollar volume can be monitored intraday on the Most Active Stocks page.
The NASDAQ 100 index closed up .27% for the day; a total of 7.03 points.
The current value is 2,647.57. priceline.com Incorporated ( PCLN ) had the largest percent change down (-5.03%) while Micron Technology, Inc. ( MU ) had the largest percent change gain rising 3.65%.
The Dow Jones index closed up .11% for the day; a total of 14.75 points.
Home Depot, Inc. (The) ( HD ) had the largest percent change down (-2.19%) while Cisco Systems, Inc. ( CSCO ) had the largest percent change gain rising 2.35%.
